    "description": "CAICA DIGITAL Inc., together with its subsidiaries, provides information technology services in Japan. The company offers system development, system consulting, and system maintenance and support; and management and support services. It is also involved in the research, development, consulting, and sale of cryptocurrency-related systems; operation of corporate support platforms and related system development; sale of software; website planning, production, and management services; investment and management of cryptocurrency; and operation of NFT sales offices. In addition, the company engages in the development and sale of communication equipment using various wireless methods; and media business that provides crypto asset-related content. The company was formerly known as CAICA Inc. and changed its name to CAICA DIGITAL Inc. in November 2021. CAICA DIGITAL Inc. was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
